details.description:
Welcome to the first bubble tea truck that started in Gaston County! We are excited to bring our bubble tea's unique and refreshing taste to Charlotte.

Our journey began with a love for bubble tea and a desire to share it with others. We saw an opportunity to bring something new and exciting, and we jumped at the chance to start our own business.

Our mission is to provide a high-quality and delicious drink option. We take pride in using only authentic ingredients and the highest quality tea leaves in our drinks. We believe that bubble tea should be more than just a drink - it should be an experience. That's why we strive to create a welcoming and friendly atmosphere for our customers.

reviews_data.review_text:
Bocha Bubble Tea: A Refreshing Delight
Bocha Bubble Tea offers a delightful and customizable bubble tea experience. Their extensive menu boasts a wide variety of flavors, from classic milk teas to innovative fruit-infused concoctions. The quality of the tea is evident in every sip, and the toppings, like the chewy tapioca pearls, add a playful texture. The staff is friendly and always willing to help you navigate the menu. Whether you're a bubble tea aficionado or a curious newcomer, Bocha is a must-try.

reviews_data.review_text: I was really looking forward to trying the bubble tea from BoCha, so I was very disappointed when my experience wound up being subpar. reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Helen,

We are sorry to hear that you did not have the experience that we intend for all our customers to have.

Please be assured that we cook our brown sugar boba fresh everyday right before coming out for the day. We strive to use the highest quality ingredients.

We would love to make it an enjoyable experience for you if you give us another chance.

It is quite possible that due to multiple toppings the drink over all turned out to be sweeter than regular. We can lower the sweetness level of the drink for you. 

Thank you for your feedback and please see us again.

Bocha Bubble Tea offers a delightful and customizable bubble tea experience. Their extensive menu boasts a wide variety of flavors, from classic milk teas to innovative fruit-infused concoctions. raw_data.name: BoCha Bubble Tea
raw_data.full_address: 3709 Oakdale Rd, Charlotte, NC 28216, United States
raw_data.description:
Welcome to the first bubble tea truck that started in Gaston County! We are excited to bring our bubble tea's unique and refreshing taste to Charlotte.

Our journey began with a love for bubble tea and a desire to share it with others. We saw an opportunity to bring something new and exciting, and we jumped at the chance to start our own business.

Our mission is to provide a high-quality and delicious drink option. We take pride in using only authentic ingredients and the highest quality tea leaves in our drinks. We believe that bubble tea should be more than just a drink - it should be an experience. That's why we strive to create a welcoming and friendly atmosphere for our customers.
